parameters.query:
SELECT 
  id, name, age, gender, contact, mail, condition_type, 
  glucose, systolic_bp, diastolic_bp, heart_rate, bmi, 
  insulin, blood_sugar, ck_mb, troponin, 
  DATE_FORMAT(visit_date, '%Y-%m-%d') as visit_date_formatted, 
  DATE_FORMAT(next_followup, '%Y-%m-%d') as next_followup_formatted, 
  assigned_doctor, status 
FROM patients 
WHERE id = {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.patient_id ?? $('Webhook').item.json.patient_id }}
LIMIT 1
